{"tid":1131595,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"瘋魔亞洲嘅劇集！呢個霸道總裁真係不得了！高甜《鐵石心腸》讓觀眾淪陷瘋狂追劇，天才男主靚仔到讓你唔撚信！","createTime":"2019-04-29T17:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T18:12:18.000Z","uid":92376,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e75065bdc6a612b0588ed77261ca54a7ed870ab2","tid":1131595,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T17:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pretty.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/thai.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpretty.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fthai.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26w%3D600&h=46e41988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你好劇荒的女生們～～今天為大家強烈推薦一部最近非常沉迷的劇集《鐵石心腸》！這部劇開播至今人氣節節上升，除了在本國Twitter被洗版外，也在全亞洲掀起了一股追劇熱潮，無論在微博和小紅書上都不時看見這部劇的各種派糖片段，現在就來看一下這部靚仔靚女霸道總裁復仇劇到底魅力何在吧！<br />\n<br />\n《鐵石心腸》劇情講述男主是位私生子，小時候被惡毒後媽逼進水裏差點溺死，後被阿姨收養，長大後改了名的他成為了高級夜總會和賭場的霸道總裁，並決心向以往曾欺負過他的人展開復仇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pretty.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1335665-0-q80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpretty.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1335665-0-q80.jpg&h=bbc11df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而女主則是個漂亮乖巧的女孩，和男主在小時候是互相扶持的青梅竹馬，長大後認出了男主，一心想阻止他的復仇計畫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://girls-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/e2b9ce0b218b42b691404d3d6ae1326a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgirls-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fe2b9ce0b218b42b691404d3d6ae1326a.gif&h=51aa91e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男主雖然在20年來一直深愛著女主，但為了報仇卻不肯承認自己的真實身分，更使計勾引女主的姊姊，展開了愛恨情仇交織的復仇故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pretty.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/photo-1-1555525474767568919117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpretty.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fphoto-1-1555525474767568919117.jpg&h=d24bb34b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怎麼樣～～劇情是不是真的超俗套超狗血，不過觀眾就是越狗血越喜歡！而且男女主是真的一個型一個靚，兩人的互動也是真的好丁！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://girls-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/n37p8q392r714419nn698r3rpq955ss9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgirls-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fn37p8q392r714419nn698r3rpq955ss9.gif&h=146d26c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://girls-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/93c6-hvscktf8258432.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgirls-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F93c6-hvscktf8258432.gif&h=99ca641c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女主完全是超善良的小白兔，對姊姊後媽的各種刁難總是忍氣吞聲，傻白甜的人設雖然老套，但真的被女主演出了一種我見猶憐的無辜感，讓人看了就忍不住想保護！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://girls-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cc5a0e53eeff4c47ae896da57e16b2ae.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgirls-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fcc5a0e53eeff4c47ae896da57e16b2ae.gif&h=0ae03f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於男主，最貼切的形容就是「青靚白淨腳又長」！185的驕人身高，和女主形成了超萌身高差，完全是「大灰狼和小白兔」的組合啊～～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://girls-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/r93s819134o747or85r613r4o5qoq70o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgirls-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fr93s819134o747or85r613r4o5qoq70o.gif&h=a86b433e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://girls-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1f921b407388453baf68fe74f5d32ef5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgirls-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1f921b407388453baf68fe74f5d32ef5.gif&h=0697cd45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飾演男主的演員是25歲的視帝Tor，後生女對於這種白臉仔長相的男生真的毫無抵抗力！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pretty.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cb1e66492685665357e6ddde224812ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpretty.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fcb1e66492685665357e6ddde224812ae.jpg&h=9c055ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pretty.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/be151c389bfecb4f99f93860ee41cdec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpretty.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fbe151c389bfecb4f99f93860ee41cdec.jpg&h=3f6fe461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩人同框的畫面不僅超養眼，而且CP感爆棚，壁咚、車咚、更衣室咚、親親抱抱等劇情更是每集都讓你看個夠！霸道總裁一言不合就親親的超甜絲絲舉動真的讓觀眾們分分鐘發晒姣出晒水！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://girls-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oq4381o11q8646n495n3rrs914459rqs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgirls-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Foq4381o11q8646n495n3rrs914459rqs.gif&h=00b93146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://girls-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1554474244-342870751.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgirls-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1554474244-342870751.gif&h=f4ada43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想看女主傷口，女主不讓，男主直接用大長腿夾住女主，然後直接靠近，最後這個壞笑簡直讓觀眾差點丁死！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pretty.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/245b3c78ce3927677e28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpretty.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F245b3c78ce3927677e28.jpg&h=4848a666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n摸頭動作也做得行雲流水～簡直好丁到爆囉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://girls-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1554432265410.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgirls-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1554432265410.gif&h=4fe187bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原link<br />\n<a href=\"https://pretty.presslogic.com/article/298246/呢個霸道總裁真係不得了-高甜泰劇-鐵石心腸-讓觀眾淪陷瘋狂追劇-天菜男主帥到讓你懷疑人生\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpretty.presslogic.com%2Farticle%2F298246%2F%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E9%9C%B8%E9%81%93%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%86-%E9%AB%98%E7%94%9C%E6%B3%B0%E5%8A%87-%E9%90%B5%E7%9F%B3%E5%BF%83%E8%85%B8-%E8%AE%93%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E6%B7%AA%E9%99%B7%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%87-%E5%A4%A9%E8%8F%9C%E7%94%B7%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%A5%E5%88%B0%E8%AE%93%E4%BD%A0%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYhq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=4b4e017d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pretty.presslogic.com/article/298246/呢個霸道總裁真係不得了-高甜泰劇-鐵石心腸-讓觀眾淪陷瘋狂追劇-天菜男主帥到讓你懷疑人生</a><br />\n<br />\n內文有部分台灣或支那流行字眼已經本人作相應修改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如仍有核突字詞 敬請原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330fa844894597e97884284b06cea4df2334fe9b","tid":1131595,"uid":136738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T18:09:34.000Z","msg":"條仔係幾正 有演技"},{"pid":"b90e7567c2f3d76746d87ffddccdae3f0953e961","tid":1131595,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"330fa844894597e97884284b06cea4df2334fe9b","tid":1131595,"uid":136738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T18:09:34.000Z","msg":"條仔係幾正 有演技"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"我睇左啲報導<br />\n話原來男主係女主既偶像<br />\n兩年前個女仔仲R緊男神合照<br />\n依家竟然可以一齊拍劇做情侶<br />\n真係幾童話feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}